textBeforeTable: March 2013 This is a list of Bulbapedia's monthly top contributors. This list is updated monthly, and is determined by the total amount of mainspace edits each user has at the end of a calendar month. This excludes all edits to talk pages, user pages, user talk pages and templates, among others. The tally is reset at the beginning of the next month; for a cumulative list of top contributors since the opening of Bulbapedia, see the top contributors.
